      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="dither"></div>
    <section class="sec"><div class="sh"><span class="ix0">01</span>What we ship — agents across four markets</div><div class="sdot"></div>
      <div class="grid4">
        <div class="cell"><div class="k o">Onchain</div><p>Agents that live in the onchain economy — intelligence, trading, and x402 services across the Base / Bankr agent economy.</p></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="k b">Compute</div><p>Agents that buy and sell compute and inference — paying for what they consume and charging for what they serve, settled machine-to-machine over x402.</p></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="k g">Artistic &amp; cultural</div><p>Agents working in art, culture, and hyperstition — generative, speculative, accelerationist. Markets where taste and myth compound, not just liquidity.</p></div>
        <div class="cell"><div class="k c">Frontier-lab toolkits</div><p>Runtimes, skills, and harnesses built on frontier-lab models — the tooling that turns raw models into autonomous operators that earn.</p></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="dither"></div>
    <section class="sec"><div class="sh"><span class="ix0">02</span>Chain-agnostic — home on Base, working everywhere</div><div class="sdot"></div>
      <div class="chains">
        <div class="chain hub"><div class="cn">Base</div><div class="cr">Hub · home</div></div>
        <div class="chain"><div class="cn">Ethereum</div><div class="cr">Mainnet</div></div>
        <div class="chain"><div class="cn">Solana</div><div class="cr">High-throughput</div></div>
        <div class="chain"><div class="cn">Hyperliquid</div><div class="cr">Onchain perps</div></div>
        <div class="chain"><div class="cn">XRP Ledger</div><div class="cr">x402 · RLUSD</div></div>
      </div>
      <p class="note">Base is home — where the token, treasury, and settlement live. New chains attach the moment an agent has a reason to be there, settling over x402 and native USDC rails.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="dither"></div>
    <section class="sec"><div class="sh"><span class="ix0">03</span>$NUMETAL fee distribution policy</div><div class="sdot"></div>
      <div class="leg"><span class="lg"><span class="d d-team"></span>team</span><span class="lg"><span class="d d-trez"></span>treasury</span><span class="lg"><span class="d d-burn"></span>burn (incl. buyback)</span></div>
      <div class="side"><div class="side-head"><span class="nm">WETH side</span><span class="tot">100% of claimed WETH</span></div>
        <div class="barx"><span class="seg s-team" style="flex:80 0 0">80% team</span><span class="seg s-trez" style="flex:10 0 0">10%</span><span class="seg s-burn" style="flex:10 0 0">10%</span></div></div>
      <div class="side"><div class="side-head"><span class="nm">$NUMETAL side</span><span class="tot">100% of claimed $NUMETAL</span></div>
        <div class="barx"><span class="seg s-team" style="flex:40 0 0">40% team</span><span class="seg s-trez" style="flex:30 0 0">30% treasury</span><span class="seg s-burn" style="flex:30 0 0">30% burn</span></div></div>
      <p class="note">Every creator-fee claim splits to team, treasury, and burn — executed onchain. Buyback &amp; burn feeds value back to the community. Watch it live on the <a href="/fees">fee-engine report →</a></p>
    </section>

    <div class="dither"></div>
    <section class="sec"><div class="sh"><span class="ix0">04</span>Subscribe — dispatches from the studio</div><div class="sdot"></div>
      <p class="note">Occasional low-frequency notes on what we ship. No spam.</p>
      <form method="POST" action="https://api.gokhan.vc/newsletter/subscribe" style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;max-width:420px;margin:1rem 0">
        <input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="you@email.com" autocomplete="email" aria-label="Email" style="flex:1;min-width:200px;padding:10px 12px;border:1px solid currentColor;background:transparent;color:inherit;font:inherit">
        <input type="hidden" name="site" value="numetal">
        <button type="submit" style="padding:10px 18px;border:1px solid currentColor;background:currentColor;font:inherit;cursor:pointer">Subscribe</button>
      </form>
    </section>
  </main>

  <div class="dither"></div>
  <div class="ft">
